\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 6. P. rubra }(Lam.) Delarbre,{\i  Fl. Auvergne} ed. 2, 553 (1800). Like {\b 4} but the cauline leaves with c. 20 lobes; flowers dark reddish-brown to purplish- or blackish-red, or reddish-violet; perianth-segments not recurved at the apex but soon spreading from the base, 2-2½ times as long as the stamens. •{\i  C. & S. France; N.E. Spain.} Ga Hs.
