\pard\f0\fs28 The plants from Spain have been described as subsp. {\b hispanica} Zimm. ex Aichele & Schwegler,{\i  Feddes Repert.}{\b  60}: 158 (1957). They differ from subsp. {\i rubra} principally in having reddish-violet flowers, and merit at most varietal rank.
